{"content":"---\ntitle: \"&lt;system.serviceModel.activation&gt; | Microsoft Docs\"\nms.custom: \"\"\nms.date: \"03/30/2017\"\nms.prod: \".net-framework\"\nms.reviewer: \"\"\nms.suite: \"\"\nms.technology: \n  - \"dotnet-clr\"\nms.tgt_pltfrm: \"\"\nms.topic: \"article\"\nms.assetid: c0cae85f-56cb-4030-8807-6f96edff8d2d\ncaps.latest.revision: 9\nauthor: \"Erikre\"\nms.author: \"erikre\"\nmanager: \"erikre\"\n---\n# &lt;system.serviceModel.activation&gt;\nThis configuration section represents the configuration settings for the SMSvcHost.exe tool. The configuration elements can be configured in the SMSvcHost.exe.config file. Specifically, it includes all machine-wide settings that must be configured.  \n  \n## Sample Configuration File  \n The following is a sample configuration file (SMSvcHost.exe.config), which is used by the listener process SMSvcHost.exe.  \n  \n```  \n<configuration>  \n   <runtime>  \n      <gcConcurrent enabled=\"false\" />  \n   </runtime>  \n   <system.serviceModel.activation>  \n       <net.tcp listenBacklog=\"10\"  \n          maxPendingAccepts=\"2\"  \n          maxPendingConnections=\"100\"  \n          receiveTimeout=\"00:00:10\"  \n          teredoEnabled=\"false\">  \n          <allowAccounts>  \n             <!-- LocalSystem account -->  \n             <add securityIdentifier=\"S-1-5-18\"/>  \n             <!-- LocalService account -->  \n             <add securityIdentifier=\"S-1-5-19\"/>  \n             <!-- Network Service account -->  \n            <add securityIdentifier=\"S-1-5-20\"/>   \n             <!-- Administrators account -->  \n            <add securityIdentifier=\"S-1-5-32-544\" />   \n             <!-- IIS_IUSRS account (Vista only) -->  \n             <add securityIdentifier=\"S-1-5-32-568\"/>  \n           </allowAccounts>  \n       </net.tcp>  \n       <net.pipe maxConnectionsPendingDispatch=\"100\"  \n          maxPendingAccepts=\"2\"  \n          receiveTimeout=\"00:00:10\">  \n          <allowAccounts>  \n             <!-- LocalSystem account -->  \n             <add securityIdentifier=\"S-1-5-18\"/>  \n             <!-- LocalService account -->  \n             <add securityIdentifier=\"S-1-5-19\"/>  \n             <!-- Network Service account -->  \n            <add securityIdentifier=\"S-1-5-20\"/>   \n             <!-- Administrators account -->  \n            <add securityIdentifier=\"S-1-5-32-544\" />   \n             <!-- IIS_IUSRS account (Vista only) -->  \n             <add securityIdentifier=\"S-1-5-32-568\"/>  \n           </allowAccounts>  \n       </net.pipe>  \n       <diagnostics performanceCountersEnabled=\"true\" />  \n   </system.serviceModel.activation>  \n</configuration>  \n```  \n  \n## See Also  \n <xref:System.ServiceModel.Activation.Configuration>","nodes":[{"pos":[12,67],"content":"&lt;system.serviceModel.activation&gt; | Microsoft Docs","needQuote":false,"needEscape":true,"nodes":[{"content":"<ph id=\"ph1\">&amp;lt;</ph>system.serviceModel.activation<ph id=\"ph2\">&amp;gt;</ph> | Microsoft Docs","pos":[0,55],"source":"&lt;system.serviceModel.activation&gt; | Microsoft Docs"}]},{"pos":[365,403],"content":"&lt;system.serviceModel.activation&gt;","linkify":"&lt;system.serviceModel.activation&gt;","nodes":[{"content":"<ph id=\"ph1\">&amp;lt;</ph>system.serviceModel.activation<ph id=\"ph2\">&amp;gt;</ph>","pos":[0,38],"source":"&lt;system.serviceModel.activation&gt;"}]},{"content":"This configuration section represents the configuration settings for the SMSvcHost.exe tool.","pos":[404,496]},{"content":"The configuration elements can be configured in the SMSvcHost.exe.config file.","pos":[497,575]},{"content":"Specifically, it includes all machine-wide settings that must be configured.","pos":[576,652]},{"pos":[661,686],"content":"Sample Configuration File","linkify":"Sample Configuration File","nodes":[{"content":"Sample Configuration File","pos":[0,25]}]},{"content":"The following is a sample configuration file (SMSvcHost.exe.config), which is used by 